		<div id="content">				<div id="post-934" class="post-934 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-themes">
			<div class="post-header">
				<div class="tags"></div>
				<h1>New Theme — 4 April to 18&nbsp;April</h1>
				<div class="author">
					<span class="by-author"><span class="sep">by</span> <span class="titan-author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="https://micfic.wordpress.com/author/rudyneeser/" title="View all posts by Rudy Neeser" rel="author">Rudy Neeser</a></span> </span>on					April 4, 2011				</div>
			</div><!--end post header-->
			<div class="entry clear">
								<p>This fortnight&#8217;s theme is:</p>
<p><a title="morningmist by Per Ola Wiberg ~ Powi, on Flickr" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/powi/1482298599/"><img class="aligncenter" src="https://i2.wp.com/farm2.static.flickr.com/1260/1482298599_e786a1e22f.jpg" alt="morningmist" width="500" height="375" /></a></p>
<p>This photograph is by Per Ola Wiberg and is licensed under <a href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/2.0/deed.en">CC By 2.0</a>.</p>
<p><strong>Edit</strong>: I&#8217;ve been informed that there is also a word count to this thing! I declare the word count to be 200 words. That is, within the range 150-250 words.</p>
<p>Enjoy!</p>
		<div class="wpcnt">
			<div class="wpa wpmrec">
				<a class="wpa-about" href="https://wordpress.com/about-these-ads/" rel="nofollow"></a>
